<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Airbnb :D</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet"href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.12.1/css/all.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
	<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.8/js/all.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-light bg-light sticky-top">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><img src="/img/logo.png" width="180" height="50"></a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/room">Room Listing</a>
                        </li>

                        <li class="nav-item">

                            <% if(ok){ %>
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Log Out</a>
                              <% } else{ %>
                                <a class="nav-link" href="/singup">Sign Up</a>
                             <% } %>
                        </li>
        
                    </ul>
                </div>
        
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div id="slides" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ul class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#slides" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#slides" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="img/mine1.png">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1 class="display-2 letra">Airbnb</h1>
                    <h3 class="letra">A place to call home,<br> far from home</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="img/mine2.png">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1 class="display-2 letra">Look some rooms</h1>
                    <a href="/room"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Go to</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="container-fluid padding">
        <div class="row welcome text-center">
            <br><hr><br>
            <!---->
            <form action="/search" class="col-12" method="POST">
                <h2 class="display-4">Book unique places to <br>stay and things to do.</h2><br><br><br>
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                    <h3 class="font-weight-bold" for="City">Where</h3>
                    <select class="form-control form-control-md" id="City" name="location">
                        <option value="Anywhere">Anywhere</option>
                        <option value="Toronto">Toronto</option>
                        <option value="Vaughan">Vaughan</option>
                        <option value="Markham">Markham</option>
                        <option value="Ottawa">Ottawa</option>
                        <option value="Waterloo">Waterloo</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold"  for="checkin">Check-in</h3>
                        <input id="checkin" type="date" name="date-in" required />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <h3 class="font-weight-bold"  for="checkout">Checkout</h3>
                        <input id="checkout" type="date" name="date-out" required />
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                    <h3 class="font-weight-bold" for="guest">Guests</h3><br>
                    <select class="form-control form-control-md" id="guest" name="guest">
                        <option value="oneguest">1 guest</option>
                        <option value="twoguest">2 guest</option>
                        <option value="threeguest">3 guest</option>
                        <option value="fourguest">4 guest</option>
                        <option value="moreguest">5 or more</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <br>
                <button id="botao" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Search</button>
                <br><br><br><br>
            </form> 
            
            <!---->
            
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1 class="display-3">Why Airbnb?</h1>
            </div><br><hr><br>
            <div class="col-12">
                <h3 class="display-4">Simple, we offer you the freedom to choose between the best places to stay, 
                    wherever you go.</h3>
            </div><br><hr><br>
            <div class="col-12">
                <p class="lead">Easy to check-in, thousands of different places to stay, with affordable prices, 
                    premium service levels and a user system of evaluation that allows you to interact 
                    with previous customers, making sure you’ll get to choose between the real best of the best. 
                    Here in Airbnb we don’t offer you just a comfortable place to stay, we offer you the experience 
                    of a lifetime, in the palm of your hand. So, the next time you’re out of town and looking for 
                    the best, just Airbnb and enjoy your stay.</p>
            </div><br><hr><br>
    
            <div class="col-12">
                <br><h1 class="display-4">Take a look at the following video:</h1><br>
                <div class="center">
                    <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
                        <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KT9zihN24bE" title="Airbnb trailer" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
    
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="container-fluid padding">
            <div class="row text-center padding">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <h3>Follow us:</h3>
                    <p>Get news in our social media, lets be friends :D</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 social padding">
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/AirbnbBrasil/" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/airbnb"  target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/airbnb/"  target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>